; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 387-398
; Tests lot matching when lots have no explicit date in their annotation.
; The code falls back to finding the earliest transaction date for the lot
; from the account's postings as a date proxy for sorting.

; Buy stock with price annotation but no date
2020/01/15 Buy Lot A
    Assets:Brokerage         5 AAPL {$100}
    Assets:Cash             -$500

2020/06/01 Sell AAPL
    Assets:Brokerage        -3 AAPL @ $150
    Assets:Cash              $450
    Income:Capital Gains

test --lot-matching fifo --lots bal Assets:Brokerage
       2 AAPL {$100}  Assets:Brokerage
end test
